reviewText: An amazing story filled with fun, surf and Jesus! You may be changed forever for the better :)

This was a great documentary. Noah Snyder was open to sharing his love for surfing, his tough life struggles and most importantly his love for God. It was uplifting and inspiring and some great surf shots.

Documentary of a young man's life surfing and finding a greater reason for life.  Great interview clips...great video of surfing.  Inspiring story of a young man and his friends quest to be great surfers and how they encounter a greater comraderie......
